data.title: S.K.I.N profile | S.K.I.Nプロフィール
data.meta_description: About visual kei band S.K.I.N: profile, biography, history. ビジュアル系バンド「S.K.I.N」プロフィール・活動 (V. GACKT / G. SUGIZO / G. MIYAVI / B. JU-KEN / D. YOSHIKI) | vkgy (ブイケージ)
data.text:
GACKT (ex.MALICE MIZER) and YOSHIKI (X JAPAN) announce that they are planning to start a band together.

The project name is announced as S.K.I.N. MIYAVI is announced as a member.

First live is held at the ANIME EXPO AX2007 in Long Beach, California, in front of 15000 people.

No additional information is given after their first live, resulting in the band being a one-time project. MIYAVI mentioned S.K.I.N as one of his "past bands" as of October 2010
